OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy throughout Tuesday evening,
OL,7,Fperhaps with the odd spot of drizzle.
OL,8,FSome clearer spells emerging as the
OL,9,Fnight progresses, turning chillier
OL,10,Funder any starry scenes but also with
OL,11,Fmist and fog forming.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FMist and fog locally
OL,14,Flingering until late morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise, a dry day with an
OL,16,Fincreasing amount of pleasant spring
OL,17,Fsunshine. Feeling mild with a gentle
OL,18,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
