OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,6,Fand very mild on Thursday, but rain
OL,7,Farrives overnight. Temperatures
OL,8,Freturning nearer to average to end the
OL,9,Fweek, with more cloud around at times
OL,10,Fas well.
